          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The dense spherical ceramic particles of about 300 mum",
                "diameter.",
                "In the case of UO2 and ThO2, spherical particles of",
                "about 300 mum diameter were filled into the stainless",
                "steel target tubes, whereas for NpO2 large spheres were",
                "first crushed to irregularly sized particles of",
                "90-300 mum.  The 2.5 X 8 mm target tubes could thus",
                "contain about 150 mg of NpO2 particles, 240 mg of ThO2",
                "and 250 mg of UO2 spheres, respectively.  The targets",
                "were filled with helium and sealed."
              ]
            }
          ],
